                <p><app loc="2"><lem resp="#robinson1913">Δένιος</lem> 
                    <rdg resp="#CIG"><supplied reason="lost">Δε</supplied>ίνιος</rdg>
                    <rdg resp="#SECir">Δίνιος</rdg>
                </app></p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Argeios fils de Deinis. Argeios fils de Deinis.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Argeios son of Deinis. Argeios son of Deinis.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Argeios figlio di Deinis. Argeios figlio di Deinis.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>أرجيوس بن دينيوس. أرجيوس بن دينيوس</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Lines 2 and 3 seem to be a clumsy attempt to repeat the original cutting.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
